@startuml Hockey Editor Use Case Diagram
title Hockey Editor Use Case Diagram

actor "Hockey Coach/Analyst" as Coach

rectangle "Hockey Editor Pro" {
    usecase "Load Video" as UC1
    usecase "Mark Attack Events" as UC2
    usecase "Mark Defense Events" as UC3
    usecase "Mark Shift Events" as UC4
    usecase "Review Timeline" as UC5
    usecase "Edit Segments" as UC6
    usecase "Preview Segments" as UC7
    usecase "Export Segments" as UC8
    usecase "Save Project" as UC9
    usecase "Load Project" as UC10
    usecase "Configure Settings" as UC11
    usecase "Customize Hotkeys" as UC12
    usecase "Undo/Redo Actions" as UC13
}

' Primary use cases
Coach --> UC1 : Open video file
Coach --> UC2 : Press 'A' key twice
Coach --> UC3 : Press 'D' key twice
Coach --> UC4 : Press 'S' key twice
Coach --> UC5 : View interactive timeline
Coach --> UC6 : Double-click segment
Coach --> UC7 : Click Preview button
Coach --> UC8 : Click Export button
Coach --> UC9 : Ctrl+S or File→Save
Coach --> UC10 : File→Open Project
Coach --> UC11 : Settings dialog
Coach --> UC12 : Settings→Hotkeys
Coach --> UC13 : Ctrl+Z / Ctrl+Shift+Z

