note right of UC2
  **Event Marking Workflow:**
  1. Video playing
  2. Press hotkey (A/D/S) - start recording
  3. Video continues playing
  4. Press same hotkey again - end recording
  5. Segment appears on timeline
end note

note right of UC5
  **Timeline Features:**
  • 3 color-coded tracks (Attack/Defense/Shift)
  • Zoom and pan support
  • Real-time playhead
  • Segment drag/resize
  • Double-click to edit
end note

note right of UC8
  **Export Options:**
  • Video segments (MP4/MOV/MKV)
  • CSV data export
  • Quality settings
  • Batch processing
end note

note as N1
  **Primary Actor Goals:**
  • **Mark Events**: Real-time event annotation during video playback
  • **Review Work**: Interactive timeline with filtering and preview
  • **Share Results**: Export segments for analysis or presentation
  • **Manage Projects**: Save/load work with version control
end note

@enduml
